<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 03:13:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>一些美国议员呼吁对新闻应用 NewsBreak 的中国血统进行更多审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/newsbreak-some-us-lawmakers-call-more-scrutiny-news-app-with-chinese-origins-2024-06-07/</link><description>在路透社报道 NewsBreak 起源于中国并使用人工智能工具制作错误报道后，三名美国议员呼吁对美国流行的新闻聚合应用程序 NewsBreak 进行更多审查。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 20:11:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/newsbreak-some-us-lawmakers-call-more-scrutiny-news-app-with-chinese-origins-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>美国研究人员称越南加快南海造岛步伐</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/vietnam-speeding-up-south-china-sea-island-building-pace-us-researchers-say-2024-06-07/</link><description>美国研究人员周五表示，越南一直在增加在南海的疏浚和垃圾填埋工作，创造的新土地数量几乎相当于前两年的总和，为创纪录的造岛年份奠定了基础。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 17:40:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/vietnam-speeding-up-south-china-sea-island-building-pace-us-researchers-say-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>Shein 首次公开募股前的魅力攻势在欧洲遇到障碍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sheins-pre-ipo-charm-offensive-hits-roadblocks-europe-2024-06-07/</link><description>随着在线快时尚零售商 Shein 在英国加大上市前的魅力攻势，欧洲零售业和立法者的抵制也越来越大。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 15:37:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sheins-pre-ipo-charm-offensive-hits-roadblocks-europe-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>普京称俄罗斯不需要使用核武器来赢得乌克兰胜利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/putin-calls-major-expansion-russian-financial-markets-cutting-use-western-2024-06-07/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周五表示，俄罗斯无需使用核武器来确保在乌克兰取得胜利，这是克里姆林宫迄今为止发出的最强烈信号，表明欧洲自第二次世界大战以来最致命的冲突不会升级为核战争。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 12:46:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/putin-calls-major-expansion-russian-financial-markets-cutting-use-western-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>强劲的就业报告和中国数据双重打击，金价下跌 3%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-prices-dip-china-central-bank-holds-off-buying-2024-06-07/</link><description>周五，强于预期的美国就业报告浇灭了人们对美国今年降息的预期，数据显示最大的消费国中国推迟了五月份的黄金购买，加剧了看跌情绪，金价加速下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 12:01:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-prices-dip-china-central-bank-holds-off-buying-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉在中国升级车载导航软件，引入车道级引导</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-upgrades-in-car-navigation-software-china-introduces-lane-level-guidance-2024-06-07/</link><description>特斯拉周五在中国发布了车载导航系统的软件升级，引入了新功能，例如在地图上显示与道路上实际车道相对应的车道标记。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 11:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-upgrades-in-car-navigation-software-china-introduces-lane-level-guidance-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>德国部长表示，德国政府考虑将供应链法暂停两年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/german-government-considers-pausing-supply-chain-law-two-years-says-minister-2024-06-07/</link><description>德国经济部长罗伯特·哈贝克周五表示，德国政府正在考虑暂停该国供应链尽职调查法两年，以减轻企业的官僚负担，直到欧洲指令生效。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 11:56:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/german-government-considers-pausing-supply-chain-law-two-years-says-minister-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>德国央行对通胀发出警告并下调2024年增长前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-central-bank-warns-inflation-cuts-2024-growth-outlook-2024-06-07/</link><description>德国央行周五表示，来自工资的上行压力意味着通胀很顽固，一天前欧洲央行宣布了自 2019 年以来的首次降息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 11:22:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-central-bank-warns-inflation-cuts-2024-growth-outlook-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>中方强烈反对美国对台军售并敦促其撤军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-strongly-opposes-us-arms-sales-taiwan-urges-withdrawal-2024-06-07/</link><description>中国国防部周五表示，中国强烈反对美国向台湾出售武器，并敦促华盛顿立即撤回这些武器。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 10:56:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-strongly-opposes-us-arms-sales-taiwan-urges-withdrawal-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦总理谢里夫在国际货币基金组织会谈前在北京会见中国国家主席习近平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-prime-minister-sharif-meets-chinas-xi-beijing-ahead-imf-talks-2024-06-07/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，中国国家主席习近平周五在北京会见了巴基斯坦总理谢赫巴兹·谢里夫，几天后巴基斯坦将提交年度预算并申请新的国际货币基金组织（IMF）贷款。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 10:10:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-prime-minister-sharif-meets-chinas-xi-beijing-ahead-imf-talks-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国检查低于 4% 的失业率，中国进口缓慢</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-graphics-2024-06-07/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 10:05:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-graphics-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国武装船只在争议岛屿附近海域巡逻激怒日本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-armed-vessels-patrol-waters-around-disputed-islands-angering-japan-2024-06-07/</link><description>周五，在四艘中国武装海警船进入东京视为其领土的水域后，日本对北京提出抗议。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 08:51:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-armed-vessels-patrol-waters-around-disputed-islands-angering-japan-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车充电部门与挪威 Otovo 合作扩大电动汽车服务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-charging-unit-teams-up-with-norways-otovo-broaden-ev-services-2024-06-07/</link><description>大众电动汽车充电装置 Elli 与挪威 Otovo 合作，提供华为 (HWT.UL) 设备，让客户将汽车与家中的太阳能和存储系统连接起来，以减少电费。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 08:42:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-charging-unit-teams-up-with-norways-otovo-broaden-ev-services-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>解说：英国法官辞职让香港法治成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/british-judges-resignations-top-court-put-hong-kong-rule-law-spotlight-2024-06-07/</link><description>周四，两名英国高级法官辞去了香港最高上诉法院的职务，因为最近 14 名著名民主活动人士在国家安全镇压中被定罪，国际社会对香港法治的担忧加剧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 08:00:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/british-judges-resignations-top-court-put-hong-kong-rule-law-spotlight-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，美国国会议员呼吁将中国宁德时代、国轩高科列入进口禁令名单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-call-add-chinas-catl-gotion-import-ban-list-wsj-reports-2024-06-07/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，一群共和党议员表示，中国电池公司宁德时代和国轩高科应立即列入美国进口禁令名单，指控其供应链使用强迫劳动。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 06:28:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-call-add-chinas-catl-gotion-import-ban-list-wsj-reports-2024-06-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>